ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce et d'industrie de la Rive-Sud (Quebec) ** Change of Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE ET D'INDUSTRIE DE LA RIVE-SUD, in Quebec, TO CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES OF ITS DISTRICT from the Verchères, Calixa-Lavallée, Saint-Amable, Sainte-Julie, Boucherville, Longueuil (y compris les arrondissements du Vieux-Longueuil, Greenfield Park et Saint-Hubert), Saint-Lambert et Brossard to Brossard, Saint-Lambert, Longueuil, Boucherville, Sainte-Julie, Saint-Amable, Verchères, Calixa-Lavallée, Contrecoeur.
AttachmentsAttachment
